    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Депозитига пул суммалари ва қимматли қоғозлар келиб тушганлиги ҳақида юридик шахс номига хабарнома</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#24}Юридик шахснинг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Юридик шахс жойлашган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уйда жойлашган</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Хабарнома юборилаётган юридик шахснинг номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Х<span class=\"leading\"></span>А Б А Р Н О М А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Хабарномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-14 structure-27\" style=\"className:14 27; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Давлат нотариал идораси рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14} </span><span class=\"structures structure-14 structure-14\" style=\"className:14 14; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}-сонли давлат нотариал идораси</span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#13}хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#26}нотариус Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#9}Юридик шахснинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Хабарнома юборилаётган юридик шахснинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ўртасида </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Юридик шахслар ўртасида тузилган Қарз шартномасининг тузилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда тузилган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Қарз шартномасини тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-17 structure-25\" style=\"className:17 25; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Давлат нотариал идораси рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17} </span><span class=\"structures structure-17 structure-17\" style=\"className:17 17; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Давлат нотариал идораси</span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#16}Хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#28}нотариус Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Қарз шартномасининг реестр рақами билан қайд этилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Қайд этилган реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> реестр рақами билан қайд этилган қарз шартномасига кўра, </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Хабарнома юборилаётган юридик шахснинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га тўланиши лозим бўлган қарз суммаси, яъни </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Депозитига қабул қилинган пулнинг миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм нотариус депозитига қабул қилинганлиги ҳақида хабар қиламан.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Юқорида кўрсатилган пул суммасини корхона ҳисоб рақамига ўтказиш учун, </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Нотариус жойлашган жойи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Нотариус жойлашган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйда жойлашган нотариал идорага банк номи ва унинг реквизитларини (ҳисоб рақам ҳақидаги маълумотларни) ёзма равишда хабар қилишингиз сўралади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Агар </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}Депозитни олиш учун қўиладиган охирги муддат</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилга қадар юқорида кўрсатилган пул суммаси олинмаса, у белгиланган тартибда давлат бюджетига ўтказиб юборилиши маълум қилинади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Нотариус_________________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center; text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">М.Ў.</span></p>\n</div></div>",
